### 409 – Sad path: active offer already exists for merchant (run after a successful 201)
POST {{baseUrl}}/offers
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "merchant_id": "b2c3d4e5-f6a7-4b8c-9d0e-1f2a3b4c5d6e",
